question: What is the rank of India in the United Nations Conference on Trade and Development's Business-to-Consumer (B2C) E-commerce Index 2019?
explanation: India ranked 73 in the United Nations Conference on Trade and Development's Business-to-Consumer (B2C) E-commerce Index 2019. India is the world’s fifth largest global destination in the retail space and it is ranked 63 in World Bank’s Doing Business 2019.
